Download TIGER shapes for Zip Code Tabulation Areas

Source: R/zcta.R
tt_zcta.Rd

Download TIGER shapes for Zip Code Tabulation Areas

Usage

tt_zcta(year = 2021)

Arguments

year

Integer year. Required. Years < 2012 are not currently supported.

Value

sf data.frame

Examples

tt_zcta()
